541
00:42:24,140 --> 00:42:25,360
Thank you!

542
00:42:26,830 --> 00:42:30,400
Oh, I shouldn't have blurted that out.

543
00:42:31,410 --> 00:42:33,760
After you said that,

544
00:42:33,840 --> 00:42:36,320
I couldn't stop thinking

545
