711
00:57:50,650 --> 00:57:51,740
Bi-soo?

712
00:57:54,470 --> 00:57:55,730
You will

713
00:57:56,740 --> 00:57:57,830
keep

714
00:57:58,710 --> 00:57:59,930
loving me the same

715
00:58:00,850 --> 00:58:02,910
tomorrow, in two days,
and a year from now, right?

